:R-HSA-446205  a            obo:GO_0009298 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "GDP-mannose is the mannose donor for the first 5 mannose addition reactions in the N-glycan precursor synthesis, and also for the synthesis of Dolichyl-phosphate-mannose involved in other mannose transfer reactions. It is synthesized from fructose 6-phosphate and GTP in three steps." ;
        rdfs:label          "Synthesis of GDP-mannose" ;
